e_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"UaWI"}]},{"client_msg_id":"8124c79f-360a-4e04-b7cc-d231f965e01c","type":"message","user":"U9S4G0LJW","text":"スナップショット側を砂場にしたい時くらいか？嬉しいの","ts":"1600885067.081900","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"PHUc"}]},{"client_msg_id":"56cf4f02-c3a8-462c-ada5-02f449e3349a","type":"message","user":"U03C71D7H","text":"せっかくスナップショット取ってるのに変わってしまったら困る気もする","ts":"1600884988.080800","team":"T03C4RC8V","reactions":[{"name":"sorena","count":1,"users":["U9S4G0LJW"]}],"replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"cP92e"}]},{"client_msg_id":"ee7d843a-9d76-4abd-911a-25bf9c9f3fdd","type":"message","user":"U03C71D7H","text":"readonly にしなかった場合、スナップショットが writable ってのがよくわからんのだよな。わかるんだけどわからんw","ts":"1600884970.080400","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"O3E"}]},{"client_msg_id":"ac10f43c-dade-4636-818e-60056f00d803","type":"message","user":"U03C71D7H","text":"`.snapshots` 自体を subvolume にしておけば、それも防げて邪魔なのは `.snapshots` ディレクトリのみになる","ts":"1600884913.079800","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"2iU"}]},{"client_msg_id":"dd10e7a5-5cf6-41ac-8bbf-e126ac8cf64b","type":"message","user":"U03C71D7H","text":"スナップショットの中に `.snapshots` ディレクトリ自体は作られてしまっているので、 `.snapshots` がただのディレクトリだった場合はスナップショット内の `.snapshots` はその下に空のディレクトリがたくさんできるわけね","ts":"1600884885.078400","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"3+Z"}]},{"client_msg_id":"a494d46e-9ea1-4fda-9c4f-0cff1d0ee987","type":"message","user":"U9S4G0LJW","text":".snapshotの中に空のディレクトリが大量にあるような状態になる","ts":"1600884816.077000","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"HqZQ"}]},{"client_msg_id":"8b582b56-88b9-4e76-a416-1de080a4031d","type":"message","user":"U03C71D7H","text":"ああ、スナップショット自体が subvolume だから中身は空になるのか","ts":"1600884808.076600","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"YpA"}]},{"client_msg_id":"f52f4331-f870-4e74-8c30-52f882a2f93d","type":"message","user":"U9S4G0LJW","text":"それもないですね","ts":"1600884789.075600","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"0BeeT"}]},{"client_msg_id":"c7174737-88fb-4308-96fb-f0cfc67166a8","type":"message","user":"U03C71D7H","text":"試してないけど、これ `.snapshot` が subvolume じゃなくてただのディレクトリの場合は、スナップショットの中に過去のスナップショットが入ってしまって延々入れ子になる、みたいになっちゃうのかな","ts":"1600884770.075300","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"E1CDW"}]},{"client_msg_id":"f84e0ebc-20fe-4ea3-89b0-b07e7ec4d621","type":"message","user":"U9S4G0LJW","text":"ですね、切り離されます","ts":"1600884761.075000","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"21H"}]},{"client_msg_id":"c49000bf-9493-4955-9086-fb140259340e","type":"message","user":"U03C71D7H","text":"あーなるほど。スナップショットはあくまで subvolume 単位なわけだから、 `/home` のスナップショットを取った際、 `.snapshot` は別の subvolume なのでスナップショットに含まれないのか","ts":"1600884732.074000","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"7m9JL"}]},{"client_msg_id":"03172234-69d1-40ef-b934-242bffb8b9fa","type":"message","user":"U9S4G0LJW","text":"あ、リードオンリーにできたのか","ts":"1600884719.073700","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"XfKq"}]},{"client_msg_id":"571d08a8-ab8a-49d1-a2dc-8491d182d2a5","type":"message","user":"U9S4G0LJW","text":"スナップショット自体に余計な物が付いてこなくて便利そう","ts":"1600884660.072400","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"e=/9"}]},{"client_msg_id":"76b24e63-9c92-42a5-88c4-e6f5df8301d6","type":"message","user":"U03C71D7H","text":"今試しに、\n\n```$ sudo btrfs subvolume create /home/.snapshots\nCreate subvolume '/home/.snapshots'\n$ sudo btrfs subvolume snapshot -r /home /home/.snapshots/2020-09-24\nCreate a readonly snapshot of '/home' in '/home/.snapshots/2020-09-24'```\nみたいなことをしてみましたが作れました (`/home/.snapshots` を subvolume にする意味があるのかはわかってない)","ts":"1600884503.071000","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"Ich7"}]},{"client_msg_id":"4fc4d67e-27a4-4f70-bfeb-9497c931b344","type":"message","user":"U03C71D7H","text":"ですね。なので私の場合、 `/home` が FS のルートなので、 `/home` 丸ごとスナップショットは取れる","ts":"1600884427.069000","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"y6K"}]},{"client_msg_id":"a6b2cd86-f164-46b2-9c19-dff131e3b058","type":"message","user":"U9S4G0LJW","text":"なのでルートに対してもスナップショットはちゃんと撮れる","ts":"1600884391.068400","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"2MV"}]},{"client_msg_id":"e31d460f-18d6-438a-a217-e319257e0650","type":"message","user":"U9S4G0LJW","text":"実はbtrfsの場合`/`自体もサブボリュームの一つになっているというのを知っておくと多少は分かりやすくなるかもしれない","ts":"1600884340.067500","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"tCZ"}]},{"client_msg_id":"d4322ec5-74f1-490f-9869-83325ab6dc82","type":"message","user":"U03C71D7H","text":"一応 `/home` は完全独立パーティションなので、 `/home` ごとバックアップ取っていってもいいっちゃいい。どうせユーザー自分だけだし","ts":"1600884241.065700","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"C6rvU"}]},{"client_msg_id":"45a8d5f7-4671-45b2-a3be-e90d9b8ac262","type":"message","user":"U03C71D7H","text":"snapshot で定期バックアップ取るとして、どこが subvolume になっているかってのは大事っぽいなぁ","ts":"1600884200.064800","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"9Ovc9"}]},{"client_msg_id":"d85b64de-b063-43ab-bfe5-827b3889d8e6","type":"message","user":"U03C71D7H","text":"`~` を subvolume にしておきたかった…","ts":"1600884125.063600","team":"T03C4RC8V","reactions":[{"name":"wakaru","count":1,"users":["U9S4G0LJW"]}],"replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"cni6"}]},{"client_msg_id":"75631867-334d-48ee-b3bd-ac187d40319c","type":"message","user":"U03C71D7H","text":"ようやくわかってきた気がする","ts":"1600884106.063200","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"Ti8FR"}]},{"client_msg_id":"d0d699ab-f872-4f91-82e1-d7799102bfa0","type":"message","user":"U03C71D7H","text":"そこがわかってなくて、イメージ湧いてなかった","ts":"1600884094.063000","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"EciS"}]},{"client_msg_id":"c8d4967f-10b3-46e4-8575-a7e7056a7dde","type":"message","user":"U9S4G0LJW","text":"実際に触れるまで全然理解できなかったな","ts":"1600884093.062900","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"vB7"}]},{"client_msg_id":"0ce6866a-c208-4ee1-91b4-438cee11739a","type":"message","user":"U9S4G0LJW","text":"パスに紐付けされていて、外見はただのディレクトリですね","ts":"1600884066.061800","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"tRwpQ"}]},{"client_msg_id":"90661c0e-3233-4d48-9fbc-28aba6adc594","type":"message","user":"U03C71D7H","text":"Btrfs の subvolume について調べていた。こいつら、マウントされた領域とは切り離されたところに作られるのかなって勝手に思ってたんですけど、作った subvolume って全部マウントした領域から見える場所に実在するディレクトリとして現れるんですね","ts":"1600883693.059800","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"jSzSf"}]}]
